channel.title: Infinity 724 - 2 Worlds! Economy and Spawn PK
channel.description:
[CENTER]Greetings [B]MoparScape[/B],
[img]http://www.infinity724.com/kethsi2-logo.png[/img]
[I]Welcome to Infinity 724[/I]
[COLOR="#FF8C00"]Infinity is yet, another little remake, touched up with some unique features, taking away that vanilla feeling from RuneScape Private Servers. We have real achievements here, and real hero's as well!
If you feel like doing a real challenge, then you should consider Infinity in your challenge list.[/COLOR]
[B]Information about the server:[/B]
[B][SIZE=5]2 Worlds!
World 1 Full Economy World 2 Spawn Pking[/SIZE][/B]
[COLOR="#FF8C00"]Infinity had a long run between 2011 and 2013, when it had it's name changed to Kethsi. Now, in 2015, we're bringing back the old Inifnity 724 feels.
[B]Let's move to the server media and features![/B]
[B]Features:[/B]
[COLOR="#FF8C00"]Full World Integration Grand Exchange (Worlds Integration Support) Clan Chats A lot of Minigames, as Pest Control, Soul Wars, Fight Pits... Quests! Yes, we have about 5 quests ready just for the beta season! Player-Owned Houses Real RuneScape Farming Abyss (Miniquest required) Full Hunter All Potions (incluiding Barbarian Mixes!) Old Items Look Support (with money pouch and toolbelt) Almost all types of teleports (Spirit Tree, Dramen Staff, Fairy Rings, All Jewelry) Better Combat Handling FULL Runecrafting (Even Combining Runes)[/COLOR]
[B][COLOR="#FF8C00"]That's just the last things I have worked in that I can remember of. We have a lot of small features from Making Pizza to Filling a Vial. From Adding Butter to your Potato to Milking a cow.[/COLOR][/B]
[B]Links:[/B]

[I]Note; Forums are not linked to game accounts![/I]

[CENTER]Greetings MoparScape,

Welcome to Infinity 724

[COLOR="#FF8C00"]Infinity is yet, another little remake, touched up with some unique features, taking away that vanilla feeling from RuneScape Private Servers. We have real achievements here, and real hero’s as well!

If you feel like doing a real challenge, then you should consider Infinity in your challenge list.[/COLOR]

Information about the server:

[B][SIZE=5]2 Worlds!

World 1 Full Economy
World 2 Spawn Pking[/SIZE][/B]

[COLOR="#FF8C00"]Infinity had a long run between 2011 and 2013, when it had it’s name changed to Kethsi. Now, in 2015, we’re bringing back the old Inifnity 724 feels.

Let’s move to the server media and features!

Features:

[COLOR="#FF8C00"]Full World Integration
Grand Exchange (Worlds Integration Support)
Clan Chats
A lot of Minigames, as Pest Control, Soul Wars, Fight Pits…
Quests! Yes, we have about 5 quests ready just for the beta season!
Player-Owned Houses
Real RuneScape Farming
Abyss (Miniquest required)
Full Hunter
All Potions (incluiding Barbarian Mixes!)
Old Items Look Support (with money pouch and toolbelt)
Almost all types of teleports (Spirit Tree, Dramen Staff, Fairy Rings, All Jewelry)
Better Combat Handling
FULL Runecrafting (Even Combining Runes)[/COLOR]

[COLOR="#FF8C00"]That’s just the last things I have worked in that I can remember of. We have a lot of small features from Making Pizza to Filling a Vial. From Adding Butter to your Potato to Milking a cow.[/COLOR]
